{{#if sendUserWelcomeAdmin}}

  <html>
    <head>
      <style>
        .container {
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 20px;
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .header {
          text-align: center;
          padding: 20px;
          background-color: #673ab7;
          color: white;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
          line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .button {
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          background-color: #673ab7;
          color: white;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 4px;
          margin: 20px 0;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='header'>
          <h1>Welcome to Edulite!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class='content'>
          <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

          <p>Welcome to Edulite! You've been granted administrative access to
            our platform.</p>

          <p>As an Edulite administrator, you'll have access to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Complete platform management dashboard</li>
            <li>User management and access control</li>
            <li>Course approval and moderation tools</li>
            <li>Analytics and reporting systems</li>
            <li>System configuration and settings</li>
          </ul>

          <p>To access your administrative dashboard, please verify your email
            address by clicking the button below:</p>

          <div
            style='background-color: #f7f7f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; position: relative;'
          >
            <span
              style='font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #333;'
            >{{token}}</span>

            <br />
            <hr />

            <div
              style='background-color: #f7f7f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;'
            >
              <p style='margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #666;'>(Select
                the token and press Ctrl+C or Cmd+C to copy)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p>Important next steps after verification:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Set up your admin profile</li>
            <li>Review platform security settings</li>
            <li>Familiarize yourself with the admin dashboard</li>
            <li>Review pending course approvals</li>
            <li>Check system analytics</li>
          </ol>

          <p>For security reasons, please ensure you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Use a strong password</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
            <li>Keep your login credentials confidential</li>
            <li>Log out after each session</li>
          </ul>

          <p>If you have any questions about your administrative
            responsibilities or need technical assistance, please contact our
            technical support team.</p>

          <p>Best regards,<br />The Edulite Team</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
  </html>
{{/if}}

